1) cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with information transmission and coding strategies in a distributed antenna system. 
2) cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as the paper discusses the communication links between the antenna terminals and the central processor. 
3) cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper proposes optimization schemes for the distributed antenna system. 
4) cs.MM (Multimedia) is possible as the paper deals with signal processing techniques for the distributed antenna system. 
5) cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is also possible as the paper proposes low-complexity versions of the CoF and RCoF schemes.
